{"tid":2500054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視貼遼寧艦滿員編隊照 反擊遭台美日軍艦打卡的窘境","createTime":"2021-04-22T10:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T11:19:56.000Z","uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6554433d5d2d2e895c97e5c9d6efd55510879744","tid":2500054,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美中海上角力升高！ 央視曝遼寧艦「1+6」滿員編隊穿第一島鏈</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/22/3508104_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F3508104_1_1.jpg&h=2b214c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n央視軍事頻道以「解放軍海軍成立72周年前夕」為題，公布遼寧艦以「1+6」編隊形式，穿越第一島鏈。（翻攝自微博＠央視軍事）<br />\n<br />\n2021/04/22 15:06<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i4.disp.cc/imgur/kTxkztoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi4.disp.cc%2Fimgur%2FkTxkztoh.jpg&h=e65abb78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衛星照片中，台灣成功級軍艦(編號3位置在中國兩艘軍艦：055和052D編號2後方監視著<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/22/3508316_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F3508316_2_1.jpg&h=10d574ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐洲太空總署地球觀測衛星哨兵2號拍攝到的南海中沙大環礁西南方的照片，其中1為遼寧號航艦，2為黃崗艦，3為呼倫湖艦，4為成都艦及太原艦，5為南昌艦，6為3艘美軍伯克級逐驅逐艦。（取自OSINT）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/22/3508316_3_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F3508316_3_1.jpg&h=ff171fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哨兵2號於4月14日拍到的遼寧艦編隊在海南島附近的衛星影像，1為遼寧號，2為052D（成都號或太原號），3是美軍伯克級驅逐艦，雙方靠得很近。（取自OSINT）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/18/phpcWPQLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F18%2FphpcWPQLn.jpg&h=f86e541f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7509560a91cb17f94495c4eb572da8bb13e7bbfd","tid":2500054,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPxvCUZW4BvNVhf7USeYN2fREsuXtomxS1iLsCTvE311V?filename=34YjJ6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34YjJ6s.png&h=dd914c73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51692dfd7807c35659e3cbc0886f5088bdbe4cb9","tid":2500054,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"得五架飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd01c3560401b1e84c234df3302af799468ae77","tid":2500054,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/niXWn8Ru-g0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FniXWn8Ru-g0&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=db5e6140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/niXWn8Ru-g0</a>"},{"pid":"30f3579dfd28da8f455d54cb19dcf799a9d3da0c","tid":2500054,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51692dfd7807c35659e3cbc0886f5088bdbe4cb9","tid":2500054,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"得五架飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/18/3115842-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F18%2F3115842-PH.jpg&h=7515a8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太多架飛機會撞在一起"},{"pid":"18789df3813f8cf6fea36e4b54c33e74e3509d61","tid":2500054,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f3579dfd28da8f455d54cb19dcf799a9d3da0c","tid":2500054,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51692dfd7807c35659e3cbc0886f5088bdbe4c